@startuml
title Convert Command Structure

rectangle "maestro convert" as convert {
}
rectangle "new [pipeline_name]" as new
rectangle "plan <pipeline_id>" as plan
rectangle "run <pipeline_id>" as run
rectangle "status <pipeline_id>" as status
rectangle "show <pipeline_id>" as show
rectangle "reset <pipeline_id>" as reset
rectangle "batch [subcommand]" as batch

rectangle "batch run" as batch_run
rectangle "batch status" as batch_status
rectangle "batch show" as batch_show
rectangle "batch report" as batch_report

convert -- new
new -- plan
plan -- run
run -- status
status -- show
show -- reset
reset -- batch

batch -- batch_run
batch -- batch_status
batch -- batch_show
batch -- batch_report

note right of convert: CLI routing through\nmaestro/commands/convert.py
note right of new: Creates new pipeline\nin .maestro/convert/
note right of plan: Generates plan with\nAI-assisted planning
note right of run: Executes conversion tasks\nwith semantic checks
note right of status: Shows pipeline status\nfrom UI facade
note right of show: Shows detailed pipeline\ninformation
note right of reset: Resets pipeline state\nin orchestrator
note right of batch: Handles multiple pipelines\nin batch operations

@enduml